# Financial Risk Market Capital Charge Foreign Exchange Risk Amount

## identifier
de8142

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, of the market risk capital charge calculated for foreign exchange risk (including gold price risk), as determined in accordance with relevant prudential standards.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=FinancialRisk.Market.CapitalChargeForeignExchangeRisk.Amount
- classification=baf/bafot/bafot.02.06
- period=instant
